<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC
    "-//Apache Software Foundation//DTD XDOC 1.0//EN"
    "http://maven.apache.org/dtd/xdoc_1_0.dtd">

<document>
  <properties>
  <title>Build Demo</title>
  </properties>
  <body>
  <section name="Building the demo">
    <p>If you want to see a running project with the taxonomy already installed, you can build the demo project.</p>
      <subsection name="Requirements">
        <ul>
          <li>Java 7 JDK</li>
          <li>Maven 3</li>
          <li>Subversion client</li>
        </ul>
      </subsection>
    <subsection name="Check out the source code and build the plugin (optional)">
      <p>
        The demo project depends on the latest snapshot (trunk) of the plugin. So you can either set the version to the
        latest release or build the plugin locally. For the latter, check out the trunk source code from the SVN repository:
      </p>
      <source>svn co https://forge.onehippo.org/svn/taxonomy/taxonomy/trunk taxonomy-trunk</source>
      <p>
        Build the project:
      </p>
      <source>cd taxonomy-trunk
mvn clean install</source>
    </subsection>
    <subsection name="Check out, build and run the demo">
      <p>
        Check out the trunk source code from the SVN repository:
      </p>
      <source>svn co https://forge.onehippo.org/svn/taxonomy/taxonomy-demo/trunk taxonomy-demo-trunk</source>
      <p>
        Build the demo project:
      </p>
      <source>mvn clean install</source>
      <p>
        Run the demo project:
      </p>
      <source>mvn -P cargo.run</source>
      </subsection>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>